    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Handy Job is a comedic sandbox adventure game where you play as a newly sentient hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What happened has happened. You wake up as a sentient hand ready to cause trouble, but your workaholic host is all about playing by the rules. Ponder the meaning of your existence and figure out the terrible mystery which brought you into this world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perform daily tasks of an office worker</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242850/extras/aaca3f400e401960a3bd82d978e82bf9.poster.avif?t=1727196812\" width=470 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242850/extras/aaca3f400e401960a3bd82d978e82bf9.webm?t=1727196812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242850/extras/aaca3f400e401960a3bd82d978e82bf9.mp4?t=1727196812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do a lot of yapping<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242850/extras/825da69684297d4c786389d36b6bbeb6.poster.avif?t=1727196812\" width=470 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242850/extras/825da69684297d4c786389d36b6bbeb6.webm?t=1727196812\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242850/extras/825da69684297d4c786389d36b6bbeb6.mp4?t=1727196812\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Break the physical limitations of the game<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay mute